牆的標貼屬非商業性宣傳品，食環署有清晰指引，非商業性宣傳品要由地政總署鑑定後，「有需要採聯合行動時，食環署才會提供人手協助相關部門清理」。"},{"pid":"45643c90a4b66f7a0ceb27ff94b1993e29566bdd","tid":1321260,"uid":24044,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T10:15:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190716/59828821?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3dt-R0MjyV1aot5YtMb6pNA0xTuH6WYt1PcOrPwAuiD31o4KzM7SH37ZQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190716%2F59828821%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3dt-R0MjyV1aot5YtMb6pNA0xTuH6WYt1PcOrPwAuiD31o4KzM7SH37ZQ&d=VPbJsUOTS2%2BU35Cb01K8cIVlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=13d570ed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190716%2F59828821%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3dt-R0MjyV1aot5YtMb6pNA0xTuH6WYt1PcOrPwAuiD31o4KzM7SH37ZQ&h=eb439768\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190716/59828821?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3dt-R0MjyV1aot5YtMb6pNA0xTuH6WYt1PcOrPwAuiD31o4KzM7SH37ZQ</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190716/large/1563252766_cf40.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190716%2Flarge%2F1563252766_cf40.jpg&h=e5b31aa0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n連儂牆喺全港各區遍地開花，不知言論自由為何物嘅保皇黨一味話要拆，好似經民聯大律師丁煌就飛咗去太古城搞簽名運動，要求民主黨太古城西區議員趙家賢拆咗佢幅連儂牆。有女途人睇唔過眼同煌理論，點知煌舉起雙手湊近女途人，狀甚恐怖，幸得熱心途人相助驅煌，煌先至敗退。<br />\n<br />\n趙家賢早前就將自己區內嘅橫額位置化身連儂牆，畀區內居民寫上心聲。點知疑似會參與區選嘅煌，噚日喺區內擺街站搞簽名運動，要求趙家賢拆咗幅連儂牆。<br />\n<br />\n有位小姐見狀，上前問煌個街站有無申請時，煌一聽到就發難，走近該名小姐不斷高聲大嗌：「太古西不要連儂牆！」位小姐當然被嚇一嚇，點知煌繼續逼近，嗰位小姐大為不滿，批評：「你（丁煌）答唔到我嘅問題，然後你兇我？」<br />\n<br />\n與此同時，一位路過嘅女士亦對煌呢啲行徑大感不滿，叫煌行開啲。被煌逼近嘅小姐亦質問煌係咪想上前非禮，煌一聽騎呢地轉台講英文：「Tell me your quality」。跟住有太古城男居民見到煌咁樣兇女途人就立即喝斥煌：「收皮啦你！你喺度阻住我哋太古城居民啊！」煌聽到後，又再九唔搭八用英文話：「Where is your mask？」男居民答佢：「我住喺太古城㗎！居民表達有乜問題啊？要唔要連（儂）牆唔係你話嘅！」<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n煌嘅行為繼續惹其他途人不滿，紛紛叫被煌威嚇嘅小姐報警，又話無人會喺選舉選煌。搞到咁，煌先至肯離開。八方打過畀電丁煌查詢，但至今未獲回覆。</span><br />\n另外，對於網上有流傳呼籲市民向食環署舉報連儂牆，署方會即時清理，食環署職工權益工會發聲明劃清界線，澄清係謠言，仲話連儂牆的標貼屬非商業性宣傳品，食環署有清晰指引，非商業性宣傳品要由地政總署鑑定後，「有需要採聯合行動時，食環署才會提供人手協助相關部門清理」。"},{"pid":"2e49e4ee8dc3d1541bb1c60eb8a938627d30d407","tid":1321260,"uid":140740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:37:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7288ea855eac6de27c6b199d35d22157b05d9514","tid":1321260,"uid":191474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e49e4ee8dc3d1541bb1c60eb8a938627d30d407","tid":1321260,"uid":140740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:37:19.000Z","msg":"push"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:43:23.000Z","msg":"試下唔好講push<br />\n講721"},{"pid":"d85e06fd1a125b7c4d757022f4b31696c600ca27","tid":1321260,"uid":191474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:44:15.000Z","msg":"有冇人一齊去facebook屌柒班廢中？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1321354\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1321354</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bd1d8218afc57d1b2aa2bab2c60692473d60a0cb","tid":1321260,"uid":67049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:45:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c867e04078985653aca5f5955f0f327d319af28e","tid":1321260,"uid":140740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7288ea855eac6de27c6b199d35d22157b05d9514","tid":1321260,"uid":191474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e49e4ee8dc3d1541bb1c60eb8a938627d30d407","tid":1321260,"uid":140740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:37:19.