7,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f7a5aa41148603ff923a8faba4d8896685b9eb3","tid":1321260,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31437a888bb7dc738872dd9712b480dd0f6f1c8c","tid":1321260,"uid":17667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T03:34:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T03:35:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T04:04:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T04:12:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95541d43c69a996c8808912e15e1717d25f59632","tid":1321260,"uid":255962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T09:02:32.000Z","msg":"條傻佬可以不理了<br />\n但係比我諗到D野.....太古西...太古西...即係代表太古選區仲有太古東<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n果然經民聯有J蝗大狀，新民黨又想空降一個騎呢博士落區，上一屆果個王振星都唔係贏新民黨好多，大家幫幫手睇下有咩做到佢，總之一票不投反送中!"},{"pid":"2cd1eadad80301adf501fe1433a2e12c5420316d","tid":1321260,"uid":264564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T11:00:45.000Z","msg":"請幫忙向大律師公會投訴丁煌騷擾和意圖非禮女途人一事<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n//轉自FB<br />\n<br />\n【#自己香港自己救】尋日我睇到經民聯成員(聲稱係)大律師嘅丁煌，喺太古城恐嚇兼意圖非禮女途人嗰條片覺得非常不安。夜晩我寫咗個 email 去比大律師公會問下可以點做？咁佢地今日覆返我啦！(以下有原文) 覆得好快，抵讚！👍👍👍<br />\n<br />\n大家一齊填個投訴表格！！！！有 #熟悉法律嘅朋友 透露，只要人夠多大律師公會就一定要處理！雖然填完仲要寄係有啲麻煩，但大家都幫手投訴，咪比呢啲核突而且係癲嘅鹹濕佬再騷擾街上面嘅女人！！！！！😠😠😠😠😠😠<br />\n<br />\n‼️表格 Download 👉👉👉4.1(b)👈👈👈<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkba.org/content/code-conduct\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkba.org%2Fcontent%2Fcode-conduct&d=VPbJsUOTS2%2BU35Cb01K8cIVlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=b4f231cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkba.org/content/code-conduct</a><br />\n<br />\n拍片嘅係呢位 Vicky Shum 小姐，原片▶️ <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Sk7oHm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Sk7oHm&d=VPbJsUOTS2%2BU35Cb01K8cIVlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=3867eee8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2Sk7oHm</a><br />\n<br />\n我個原 po 係呢度▶️ <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2XL7VrV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2XL7VrV&d=VPbJsUOTS2%2BU35Cb01K8cIVlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=9e5641c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2XL7VrV</a><br />\n<br />\n======================<br />\n<br />\n(以下為大律師公會回覆原文)<br />\n<br />\n先生/女士 閣下︰<br />\n<br />\n就 閣下提出投訴大律師操守一事，為協助本會紀律委員會就投訴展開正式調查，本會現隨函附上投訴表格以便 閣下作出正式投訴，敬希 閣下填妥隨本電郵附上的投訴表格，並將之親身遞交或郵寄至本會秘書處（地址：香港金鐘道38號高等法院低層二樓）。本會並附上一份「投訴大律師」單張予 閣下參考。<br />\n<br />\n閣下可以在交回填妥的投訴表格時，一併提交其他有助本會調查投訴的進一步資料。<br />\n<br />\n香港大律師公會<br />\n香港金鐘道38號<br />\n高等法院低層二樓<br />\n<br />\nTel: (852) 28690210 / Direct: (852) 29789189<br />\nFax: (852) 28690189"},{"pid":"6e10dd774bce4a5efe1c942e69fc70fa8034f3e7","tid":1321260,"uid":100766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T11:42:25.000Z","msg":"好核突囉件肥豬 成件Av痴漢男主咁<br />\n隔住個mon都覺得比佢視姦緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}